Package: omixVizR
Title: 'omixVizR': Omics Visualization Toolkit
Version: 1.0.3
Authors@R: 
    person("Zhen", "Lu", , "luzh29@mail2.sysu.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3481-6310"))
Description: Comprehensive visualization of multi-omics data, including genomics, transcriptomics, and proteomics.
    Provides user-friendly functions to generate publication-quality plots, facilitating the exploration and interpretation of complex biological datasets.
    The package supports integration with popular R visualization frameworks and is suitable for both exploratory data analysis and result presentation.
